rows.name: Wow! You really found my treasure!

rows.label: qst002603_msg002
rows.name:
Thank goodness... I was
wondering what I'd do if you
couldn't find it. Thank you!

rows.label: qst002603_msg003
rows.name: Oh! I'll give you this as thanks!

rows.label: qst002603_msg004
rows.name:
Hehe, isn't it pretty?
It's my favorite!

rows.label: qst002603_msg005
rows.name:
I want to grow up to be a
cool adult who can help
people in trouble too!

rows.label: qst002603_msg006
rows.name:
Next time we meet, let's
play in the snow together!
